{
  "chapter": 7,
  "chapter_summary": "飞蛾行动进入高潮。铁大爷与慕容对峙，揭露慕容并非慕容家血脉，而是林家过继的表亲——林还玉的嫡亲兄弟。一老一少年的讨论深入核心：楚留香可能假死，飞蛾行动的真正目的是将慕容置于死地，迫使楚留香为兑现对林还玉的承诺而复活。小苏被揭露为训练有素的杀手，正是她杀了柳明秋。兰花毒烟再次出现，铁大爷中毒后被割头小鬼割走头颅。慕容面临生死边缘，等待那个欠他一条命的人来救他。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你不该来的，",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "虽然你是条好汉，可是你实在不该来的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "因为我要找的是上一代的慕容，不是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "何况你根本不是慕容家的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我调查过你，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我对你的了解，大概要比你想像中多得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你不但是条好汉，也是个人才，在少年时就曾经替慕容家策划过很多件大事，成绩都不错，所以慕容家这次才会选中你继承他们的门户。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "所以我才想不通。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "什么事想不通?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我实在想不通这次你为什么一定要来送死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "这一次你不但计划欠周密，行动更疏忍，简直就像是故意来送死的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "不管怎么样，你是个有勇气的人，像你这种人，在江湖中已不多了。",
      "tone": "赞赏",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 571,
      "line_end": 573
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "何况你并不是慕容家的人，我与你之间，并没有直接的仇恨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 577
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我也并不是一个喜欢杀人的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 577,
      "line_end": 579
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "你这是什么意思?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 581,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我的意思只不过是说，我并不一定要杀你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 583
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "我只要你给我一点面子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 583,
      "line_end": 585
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "你难道不知道江南慕容是从来不给人面子的?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 587,
      "line_end": 587
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "你难道真的想死?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 589,
      "line_end": 589
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "生又如何?死又何妨?",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 591,
      "line_end": 591
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "speaker_name": "铁大爷",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong",
      "text": "只可惜死也并不是件容易的事，我若偏不让你死，你又能怎么样?",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 593,
      "line_end": 593
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong",
      "speaker_name": "慕容",
      "listener": "char_tie_da_ye",
      "text": "我不能怎么样，可是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 7,
      "line_start": 595,
      "line_end": 595
    }
  ],
